
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Food Connect Navbar</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome for icons -->
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <style>
        .navbar {
            background-color: #f8f9fa; /* Light background for contrast */
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-item .nav-link {
            color: #000; /* Black text color for better visibility */
            padding: 15px;
        }

            .navbar-nav .nav-item .nav-link:hover {
                color: #007bff; /* Change color on hover for a nice effect */
            }

        .dropdown-menu a {
            color: #333;
        }

        .notification-bell {
            position: relative;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .notification-bell .badge {
                position: absolute;
                top: -5px;
                right: -10px;
                background: red;
                color: white;
                border-radius: 50%;
                padding: 5px 8px;
                font-size: 10px;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Food Connect</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNavDropdown" aria-controls="navbarNavDropdown" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavDropdown">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                <!-- Dropdown for Profile -->
                <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                    <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="profileDropdown" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                        Profile
                    </a>
                    <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="profileDropdown">
                        <a class="dropdown-item" asp-action="ViewProfile" asp-controller="User">View Profile</a>
                        <a class="dropdown-item" asp-action="UpdateProfile" asp-controller="User">Edit Profile</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <!-- Donate Food Dropdown -->
                <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                    <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="donateFoodDropdown" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                        Donate Food
                    </a>
                    <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="donateFoodDropdown">
                        <a class="dropdown-item"  asp-page="/CreateDonation">Make a Donation</a>
                        <a class="dropdown-item"  asp-page="/ViewDonationCategory">View Donations</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <!-- Other Navigation Items -->
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Donation" asp-action="GetClaimedDonations">Track Food Donated</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" asp-action="ReceiveFoodDonation" asp-controller="Donation">Receive Food Donation</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">View Reviews</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link notification-bell" href="#">
                        <i class="fas fa-bell"></i>
                        <span class="badge">3</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="ftco-footer ftco-section img">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="ftco-footer-widget mb-4">
                        <h2 class="ftco-heading-2">About Us</h2>
                        <p>Far far away, behind the word mountains, far from the countries Vokalia and Consonantia, there live the blind texts.</p>
                        <ul class="ftco-footer-social list-unstyled float-md-left float-lft mt-5">
                            <li class="ftco-animate"><a href="#"><span class="icon-twitter"></span></a></li>
                            <li class="ftco-animate"><a href="#"><span class="icon-facebook"></span></a></li>
                            <li class="ftco-animate"><a href="#"><span class="icon-instagram"></span></a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="ftco-footer-widget mb-4">
                        <h2 class="ftco-heading-2">Recent Blog</h2>
                        <div class="block-21 mb-4 d-flex">
